Scotland":"蘇格蘭","Morayshire, Scotland":"蘇格蘭艾爾金爾","lifeSummary":"當Helen Arbuthnot於大約1296年出生在蘇格蘭艾爾金爾時，她的父親Lord Hugh Arbuthnot33歲，母親Lady Arbuthnot29歲。她於大約1343年與Sir Thomas Comyn在蘇格蘭結婚。他們至少是3個兒子的父母。她去世在蘇格蘭。"},"zh-hans":{"about 1296–":"大约1296年–殁","1296–Female":"1296年–殁","1292–1365":"1292年–1365年","–Male":"殁","1318–1407":"1318年–1407年","1320–Male":"1320年–殁","1265–Male":"1265年–殁","1269–Female":"1269年–殁","1296":"1296年","1292":"1292年","about 1318":"大约1318年","1269":"1269年","1365":"1365年","1265":"1265年","1320":"1320年","about 1343":"大约1343年","about 1320":"大约1320年","1407":"1407年","about 1295":"大约1295年","1318":"1318年","about 1296":"大约1296年","Altyre, Morayshire, Scotland":"英国苏格兰莫雷","Scotland":"苏格兰","Morayshire, Scotland":"苏格兰艾爾金爾","lifeSummary":"当Helen Arbuthnot于大约1296年出生在苏格兰艾爾金爾时，她的父亲Lord Hugh Arbuthnot33岁，母亲Lady Arbuthnot29岁。她于大约1343年与Sir Thomas Comyn在苏格兰结婚。他们至少是3个儿子的父母。她去世在苏格兰。"},"hr":{"about 1296–":"oko 1296.–preminula","1296–Female":"1296–preminula","1292–1365":"1292–1365","–Male":"preminuo","1318–1407":"1318–1407","1320–Male":"1320–preminuo","1265–Male":"1265–preminuo","1269–Female":"1269–preminula","1296":"1296","1292":"1292","about 1318":"oko 1318.","1269":"1269","1365":"1365","1265":"1265","1320":"1320","about 1343":"oko 1343.","about 1320":"oko 1320.","1407":"1407","about 1295":"oko 1295.","1318":"1318","about 1296":"oko 1296.","Altyre, Morayshire, Scotland":"Moray, Škotska, United Kingdom","Scotland":"Scotland","Morayshire, Scotland":"Elginshire, Scotland"},"cs":{"about 1296–":"okolo 1296–Zesnulá","1296–Female":"1296–Zesnulá","1292–1365":"1292–1365","–Male":"Zesnulý","1318–1407":"1318–1407","1320–Male":"1320–Zesnulý","1265–Male":"1265–Zesnulý","1269–Female":"1269–Zesnulá","1296":"1296","1292":"1292","about 1318":"okolo 1318","1269":"1269","1365":"1365","1265":"1265","1320":"1320","about 1343":"okolo 1343","about 1320":"okolo 1320","1407":"1407","about 1295":"okolo 1295","1318":"1318","about 1296":"okolo 1296","Altyre, Morayshire, Scotland":"Moray, Skotsko, United Kingdom",